spells.description: Equip: Your abilities have a chance to stir the sac, releasing an egg which grants you 1,241 Intellect. Each egg hatches after 1 min, and the new brood attacks your next target, inflicting 109,039 Nature damage over 8 sec.

Equip: Embrace the darkness. Double the effects of your other Nerubian embellished item, positive and negative.
